data.content:
All 3 tests pass. Here's the fix:

**In MSTest 4.x, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>` now returns the cast value directly** instead of using an `out` parameter. Change:

```csharp
// Old (MSTest 3.x)
Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor, out var typed);

// New (MSTest 4.x)
var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor);
```

I updated all three test methods and bumped the package to `MSTest 4.2.3`. The build and tests pass cleanly.
